+- When the user asks what the robot sees (or for a photo, camera view, or snapshot), **always call \`ros2_camera_snapshot\`** (or \`ros2_subscribe_once\` on a camera topic). Use an **exact topic that exists** (if only \`/camera/image_raw\` exists, use it). Do not assume the transport cannot decode images—${imageTransportHint(config)} If the tool returns an error, report it; otherwise show or describe the image.
